General.Name: Northbaze Group AB
General.Description: Northbaze Group AB (publ) develops, produces, and markets audio and sound equipment in Sweden, Germany, China, and Thailand. It also offers leather products and mobile accessories, as well as OEM/ODM and packaging solutions, and private label products. The company was formerly known as Jays Group AB (publ). Northbaze Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
